@SitAiInterface_HostAddress = http://localhost:5292

### First question
POST {{SitAiInterface_HostAddress}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    { "role": "User", "content": "Hvor kan jeg leie studentbolig i Trondheim?" }
  ]
}

###

### Follow-up question
POST {{SitAiInterface_HostAddress}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    { "role": "User",      "content": "Hvor kan jeg leie studentbolig i Trondheim?" },
    { "role": "Assistant", "content": "SIT tilbyr studentboliger i Trondheim på steder som Berg Studentby og Nedre Berg..." },
    { "role": "User",      "content": "Hva koster det?" }
  ]
}

###

### Off-topic (should be rejected)
POST {{SitAiInterface_HostAddress}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [
    { "role": "User", "content": "What is the weather in Oslo today?" }
  ]
}

